data.value:
An unexpected error has unfortunately occurred and the Logbook must shut down. The details of the error are listed below. These can be either copied and pasted to an email to the developer at chris@kitchengeeks.net, or it will be available in a subdirectory titled "Error Reports" where this application is located. The file will contain copies of your Players and Tournaments, as well.
You may restart the application or close it entirely. Your progress should have been saved.
